➜美联航航班延误百余名中国乘客被拒登机，领馆称敦促航司妥善处理
http://www.sohu.com/a/413692912_161795	25415
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'210411596',
